{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"难以想到的事情","authors":["张克新"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":11,"day":25}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"难以想到的事情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张克新"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山鹰不敢歇翅的岩上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有我阿妈的脚印；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去她给奴隶主背过多少桶水？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只需看看那脚印的浅深。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今河水从岩底翻山过岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就是岩边抽水的人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿妈抱住我笑出满眼泪水："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的后生呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁给了你这大的本领？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要河水自己爬上山来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这真是难以想到的事情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荒坡上长起了荞麦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青葱葱象一片绿云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荞麦的产量有多少？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请看社里的粮仓多么丰盈；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前天又来了马拉耕播机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驾机器的就是我的爱人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进民族学院学习才一年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她咋就学会了这大的本领！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又惊又喜我忙去扶来阿妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿妈揩了九次眼泪才看清："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的后生呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这真是难以想到的事情！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}